    "innovation": {
      "type": "product-innovation",
      "settings": {
        "heading": "Innovation Meets Passion",
        "subheading": "Made in the USA",
        "text": "<p>Founded in 2013 by Mike Le, Kinetic Motorcycles was built on a simple belief: motorcycle parts aren't generic hardware — they're personal. Every product begins as an original idea, designed by Mike and developed entirely in-house.</p><p>We don't rely on templates or outsourced shortcuts. Each part is shipped by hands-on fabrication experience and time spent riding, testing, and refining. Whether you're dialing in a daily rider or building something truly your own, our focus is the same — create parts that feel intentional, functional, and worthy of your motorcycle.</p>"
      }
